etcd version 3
-----------------------
etcdctl snapshot save 
etcdctl endpoint health
etcdctl get
etcdctl put


kubectl
-------
1. kubectl config set-context $(kubectl config current-context) --namespace=dev


Taint commands
--------------
1. kubectl taint nodes node-name key=value:taint-effect
   here taint-effect can be three types
        - NoSchedule - No new pod will be schedule on this node
        - PreferNoSchedule - system will not schedule pod on this node but do not gurantee
        - NoExecute  - No new pod will be schedule on this node and existing will be evicted if they are not taint tolerant


- kubectl label node <node-name> <key>=<value> -> To label a node
